results.name: Expansion of the polynomial x^36*(x^12-1)*(x^9-1)*(x^8-1)*(x^6-1)*(x^5-1)*(x^2-1) in increasing powers of x.
comment: q^36*(q^12-1)*(q^9-1)*(q^8-1)*(q^6-1)*(q^5-1)*(q^2-1) is the order of the simple group E_6(q), if q is a prime power.
reference: R. L. Griess, Jr., Twelve Sporadic Groups, Springer, 1998; see p. 169.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 26 2010
